title: Phase II Babies Born Healthy Recap
summary: This meeting focuses on the Baby's Born Healthy program and the integration of next-gen systems for case management. Participants discuss the workflow requirements, the need for non-billable services, and the challenges faced in data transfer and documentation.

keyPoints.text: Introduction of next-gen requirements for the program
Discussion on case management needs without triggering billing
Importance of setting up non-billable appointment templates
Plan for information transfer during system build
Collaboration on documentation and workflow expectations
